  <brief_title>Topical Treatment of Scalp Psoriasis With the Fixed Combination of Calcipotriol and Betamethason (Xamiol® Gel)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Topical Treatment of Scalp Psoriasis With the Fixed Combination of Calcipotriol and Betamethason (Xamiol® Gel)</official_title>
