  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This non-interventional, prospective, non-controlled study of Xamiol® Gel, a fixed
      combination of calcipotriol and betamethason dipropionate, shall investigate in daily routine
      the efficacy, tolerability and changes in quality-of-life parameters in patients with scalp
      psoriasis
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
